  {
   "i": 31,
   "en": "...Looks like it's too soon."
  },
  {
   "i": 32,
   "en": "Fine, we'll let it go for today."
  },
  {
   "i": 33,
   "en": "The song can wait. For now, let's at"
  },
  {
   "i": 34,
