  },
  {
   "i": 41,
   "en": "Then let me teach you."
  },
  {
   "i": 42,
   "en": "When YOU stand on stage, stage left is"
  },
  {
   "i": 43,
   "en": "your left; stage right is your right."
  },
  {
   "i": 44,
   "en": "Got it? Then look toward stage left."
