   "en": "Correct. The other side is stage right."
  },
  {
   "i": 47,
   "en": "That's stage right, remember?"
  },
  {
   "i": 48,
   "en": "Stage left is your left."
  },
  {
   "i": 49,
   "en": "I got it wrong..."
  },
  {
   "i": 50,
   "en": "Uuu..."
  },
  {
   "i": 51,
   "en": "Don't make that face."
  },
  {
   "i": 52,
   "en": "Did you get mixed up?"
  },
  {
